The output should be a JSON dict (do not include markdown code blocks).
{ "story_structure": String
, "chapters": []
}

The "chapters" list will contain the outline of the plot.
Each chapter in the "chapters" list should be a JSON dictionary with the following keys:
- "name": the name of the chapter in English
- "element": the name of the element in the story structure
- "plot": a 2-5 sentence plot description that is guided by the element from the story_structure; the description should be specific (for example, don't say "the characters face challenges", describe exactly which characters face challenges and what they are and why they are important
